A couple has been arrested after allegedly killing their 8-year-old daughter during a domestic fight at Majengo estate in Kilgoris, Narok County. According to a police report, the man – in an attempt to hit his wife with a wooden object – missed and instead hit their 8-year-old daughter. The couple, Esther Kaiseyi (21) and Amos Maengwe (30), then reportedly carried their daughter to hospital for medical attention. They ran into police officers who helped them rush the child to the Kilgoris sub-county hospital. “Upon arrival at the facility, doctors tried to attend to the girl whose condition had worsened, but unfortunately she lost her life while undergoing treatment,” read the police report. The parents are presently being held at the Kilgoris Police Station awaiting arraignment as investigations continue. Also Read: Video Of The Day: Former sports CS Hassan Wario convicted over Rio games scam